      "content": "hey so i was just cutting up some veggies and the knife slipped, i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s kind of oozing blood and won't really stop. i dont want to go to the ER if i dont have to, can i just put some honey on it and wrap it up with a bandage? i heard that works for healing wounds.",
